## âœ¨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| ğŸ“„ **AI Resume Generation** | Auto-generates ATS-optimized resume with action verbs, bullet points, and keyword matching |
| âœ‰ï¸ **Cover Letter Generator** | Personalized cover letter tailored to company & job description |
| ğŸŒ **Portfolio Builder** | Structured portfolio with project cards, skill charts, and bio |
| ğŸ“Š **ATS Score Checker** | Scores resume against job description with detailed breakdown |
| ğŸ¯ **Skill Gap Analysis** | Identifies missing skills and provides a learning roadmap |
| ğŸ” **Keyword Extraction** | TF-IDF based keyword matching between resume and JD |
| ğŸ·ï¸ **Domain Classification** | Classifies resume domain (SWE, ML, DevOps, Mobile, etc.) |
| âœï¸ **Bullet Point Enhancer** | Scores and improves experience bullets using STAR method |

